Publication Date:  August 1997

Writers:  Derek Kirk and Tom Sniegoski
Artists:  Michael Lacombe and Eric Powell
Letterers:  Michael Lacombe and The Eye
Cover Artist:  Derek Kirk

Captain Oga and his police officers are still sorting through the rubble of Hiroshima (damaged in the explosion that took place at the end of Warrior Nun Areala: Rituals #6) cleaning up any Oni still left alive. Ninja Nun drops by to prevent a massacre by one pernicious Oni, and Officer Yoshida discovers the unconscious body of a beautiful woman with jade-coloured hair...

Thanks goes to Talon for this release.

